\pard\f0\fs28   Extremely variable in leaf-shape. J. Gamisans ({\i Candollea}{\b  27}: 189-209 (1972)) recognizes two subspecies based on different degrees of leaf-dissection, but intermediates occur and varietal status seems preferable.
